Summary: walking dog.looking around up noticing a cloud cover.walking back to entrance of house and saw over the tree line approx 1/2 mile or less away large object with 4 or 5 white lights in a shape of a trapazoide and smaller light shining between the larger .
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking the dog out for the night approx.930 pm.I was looking at the cloud cover and wondering if was going to snow or what have you .the cloud cover was low.when he was done going we started to head in and i notice a very large object just over the trees in a trapazoid shape 4 or 5 lights on the edges and every so often a beam or smaller lights would connect the bigger ones.this object was moving extremely slow and thought it was going to land in fields but it kept going, sinking beyond the tree line at a distance.
